creator: jark@10g.pl
text:
Hello,

I can't build apache from .tar.gz. The same is from FreeBSD's ports.

# uname -r
5.2.1-RELEASE-p3

Here is full output. Sorry for length, but errors are from the begin. I runs
./configure without any params to make it clear. I tried to run ./configure with
correct params for freebsd and also with freebsd patchs (port:
/usr/ports/www/apache13) but it has the same errors.

Thanks for help,
JG
